        <p class="hero-strap">Abdul is 38, works full-time, has young kids, and knows heart trouble runs in his family. The NHS App nudges him toward a home test that catches cardiovascular risk markers nobody else was going to find. <strong>This is the story of how the cohort gets identified before the symptoms show up.</strong></p>
