    <div class="stage" id="stage-2">
      <div class="stage-side"><div class="stage-number">02</div></div>
      <div class="stage-main">
        <div class="stage-eyebrow">Identification — the NHS App finds him</div>
        <h2 class="stage-title">The NHS App surfaces a CVKM home-test offer to Abdul based on his demographic and family-history flags. He sees it the next time he opens the app to look at his prescription. The cohort has just met the platform that can act on it. <span class="hm-witness" data-moment="abdul-s2"></span></h2>

