          <div class="stage-image-caption">illustration to follow &middot; identification stage</div>
        </div>

        <div class="pull-quote">
          <p class="pull-quote-text">I opened the app to check my repeat prescription. The home test offer was sitting on the home screen. I thought, why not, it&apos;s a Saturday job.</p>
          <div class="pull-quote-attribution">Abdul</div>
        </div>

        <div class="whats-happening">
          <div class="whats-happening-label">What is happening</div>
          <div class="whats-happening-body">39 million people are registered on the NHS App, with 62.3 million logins in a single month. Targeted cohort surfacing through the App is the highest-reach mechanism the system has for self-initiated patients.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="old-way">
          <div class="old-way-label">The old way</div>
