    <!-- STAGE 5 -->
    <div class="stage" id="stage-5">
      <div class="stage-side"><div class="stage-number">05</div></div>
      <div class="stage-main">
        <div class="stage-eyebrow">Long-term optimisation — the cycle that fits his life</div>
        <h2 class="stage-title">Abdul moves into ongoing monitoring. Blood-pressure readings via the NHS App. Annual home cholesterol re-test on a calendar reminder. The cohort he belongs to is now visible to the system, and visible to him. The next time something shifts, the system sees it; not five years late at A&amp;E. <span class="hm-witness" data-moment="abdul-s5"></span></h2>

        <div class="stage-image">
          <div class="stage-image-icon">&#x1F4DD;</div>
